<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation - STEM Mantra</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .logo span {
      color: #FFC107;
    }
    .order-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .success-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .success-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background-color: #10b981;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      font-size: 40px;
    }
    .success-title {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .success-subtitle {
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .order-info {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .order-info-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .order-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .order-value {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .order-items {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .section-title span {
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .item-details {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .item-name {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .item-meta {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .item-price {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .price-summary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2d2d44 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .price-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .price-row.total {
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FFC107;
    }
    .payment-info {
      background-color: #f0f9ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066FF;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .payment-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0066FF;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .payment-text {
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .next-steps {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .step-number {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066FF 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-right: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .step-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .step-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .step-description {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066FF 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #e2e8f0, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .help-text {
      text-align: center;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .help-text a {
      color: #0066FF;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer-logo span {
      color: #FFC107;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer-address {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">STEM <span>Mantra</span></div>
      <div class="order-badge">âœ… Order Confirmed</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="success-section">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
      <h1 class="success-title">Thank You for Your Order!</h1>
      <p class="success-subtitle">Your order has been successfully placed</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="order-info">
        <div class="order-info-header">
          <div>
            <div class="order-label">Order Number</div>
            <div class="order-value">#<%= orderId %></div>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: right;">
            <div class="order-label">Order Date</div>
            <div class="order-value"><%= new Date(orderDate).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'short', year: 'numeric' }) %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <div class="order-label">Ordered By</div>
          <div class="order-value"><%= customerName %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="order-items">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span>ðŸ“¦</span> Order Details</h2>
        <% if (items && items.length > 0) { %>
          <% items.forEach(function(item) { %>
            <div class="item">
              <div class="item-details">
                <div class="item-name"><%= item.name %></div>
                <div class="item-meta">Qty: <%= item.quantity %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="item-price">â‚¹<%= item.price.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></div>
            </div>
          <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="item-details">
              <div class="item-name"><%= productName || 'Course/Product' %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">â‚¹<%= amount ? amount.toLocaleString('en-IN') : '0' %></div>
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="price-summary">
        <div class="price-row">
          <span>Subtotal</span>
          <span>â‚¹<%= (subtotal || amount || 0).toLocaleString('en-IN') %></span>
        </div>
        <% if (discount) { %>
        <div class="price-row">
          <span>Discount</span>
          <span style="color: #10b981;">-â‚¹<%= discount.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></span>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (tax) { %>
        <div class="price-row">
          <span>Tax (GST)</span>
          <span>â‚¹<%= tax.toLocaleString('en-IN') %></span>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="price-row total">
          <span>Total Paid</span>
          <span>â‚¹<%= (total || amount || 0).toLocaleString('en-IN') %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="payment-info">
        <div class="payment-title">ðŸ’³ Payment Information</div>
        <div class="payment-text">
          Payment Method: <%= paymentMethod || 'Online Payment' %><br>
          Transaction ID: <%= transactionId || 'N/A' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="next-steps">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span>ðŸš€</span> What's Next?</h2>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Access Your Dashboard</div>
            <div class="step-description">Log in to your account to access your purchased courses and materials.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Start Learning</div>
            <div class="step-description">Begin your STEM journey with hands-on projects and expert guidance.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Get Certified</div>
            <div class="step-description">Complete your course and earn your certificate of achievement.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl || 'https://stemmantra.com/dashboard' %>" class="cta-button">
          Go to Dashboard â†’
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="divider"></div>
      
      <p class="help-text">
        Questions about your order? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@stemmantra.com">support@stemmantra.com</a>
        or call <a href="tel:+916356631515">+91-6356631515</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">STEM <span>Mantra</span></div>
      <div class="footer-text">
        Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> STEM Mantra. All rights reserved.
      </div>
      <div class="footer-address">
        C-104 2nd Floor, Noida Sec-10, UP â€“ 201301 | +91-6356631515
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
